############## root window #######3
# Pager
Key 1 A 4 MoveToPage 0 0
Key 2 A 4 MoveToPage 1 0
Key 3 A 4 MoveToPage 2 0
Key 4 A 4 MoveToPage 3 0

Key Right A CM GotoRightPage
Key Left A CM GotoLeftPage


# Minimal windows.
Key D A 4 FuncFvwmIconifyToggle
Key D A CM All (AcceptsFocus CurrentPage !Iconic !Shaded, !FvwmButtons, !"xdaliclock" !"*Desk *" !"*FvwmDocker*" !"Tild*" !"*sv*")Iconify

Key F A 4 FuncFullScreen
Key space A 4 Maximize

Key F1 A 4 Exec wcmd
Key F2 A 4 Exec devhelp
Key F3 A 4 Exec goldendict
Key F8 A 4 Module FvwmConsole
Key F12 A 4 Exec firefox
Key F11 A 4 Exec chromium --disk-cache-dir=/dev/null

Key F1 A M Menu MenuFvwmRoot
Key F12 A C Exec emacs
Key F2 A M Exec exec grun
Key F4 A M Close

Key Tab A M WindowList (CurrentPage) Root c c NoDeskSort, SelectOnRelease Meta_L,CurrentAtEnd, IconifiedAtEnd

Key r A CM Exec exec grun
Key t A MC Exec sakura

# Lock screens
Key L A 4 FuncFvwmLockScreen
Key L A CM FuncFvwmLockScreen

Key Print A N Exec exec scrot /tmp/'%Y-%m-%d.png'
Key Print A S Exec exec scrot "/tmp/$[w.id]_%H-%M-%S.png"
Key Print A M Exec exec scrot -s "/tmp/$[w.id]_%H-%M-%S.png"

Key t A 4 Exec exec xterm
Key Pause A C ExitMenu
